Package eu.cqse.check.framework.shallowparser.framework

This package provides the basic framework we use for implementing the shallow parsers.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INameResolver<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A name resolver can be passed to RecognizerBase.createNode(EShallowEntityType, Object, Object) and resolves the name of the new created entity.
    IShallowEntityVisitor
    Visitor interface for traversal of entities.
    SequenceRecognizer.ITokenMatcher
    Interface of a custom matcher.
    ShallowEntityTraversalUtils.IShallowEntityKeyVisitor
    Empty default implementation of IShallowEntityVisitor.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllLowercaseIdentifierMatcher
    Matches identifiers that contains only lowercase letters
    ExactIdentifierMatcher
    Matcher for identifiers by name.
    NotPreconditionRecognizer<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A recognizer that tries to match a prepared recognizer once but does not advance the parsing state.
    ParserState<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    This class holds the parser state and also implements parts of the parsing algorithm.
    PreconditionRecognizer<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A recognizer that allows to match a prepared recognizer once but does not advance the parsing state.
    PropertyAccessNameResolver<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    Resolves the name of a getter or setter for a CS property.
    RecognizerBase<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A node used for recognizing a part of the system.
    RecognizerUtils
    Utility methods for writing recognizers.
    SequenceRecognizer<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A recognizer for sequences.
    ShallowEntity
    An entity resulting from shallow parsing.
    ShallowEntityTraversalUtils
    Utility methods for working with shallow entities.
    ShallowEntityTraversalUtils.CollectingVisitorBase
    Base class for visitors that collect shallow entities.
    ShallowEntityTraversalUtils.ShallowEntityVisitorBase
    Empty default implementation of IShallowEntityVisitor.
    ShallowParserBase<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    Base class for shallow parsers that implements most of the generic parsing logic.
    ShallowParserRuleProviderBase<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>,PARSER extends ShallowParserBase<STATE>>
    Base class for rule extenders, i.e., classes that contribute parsing rules to a shallow parser.
    SubRecognizer<STATE extends java.lang.Enum<STATE>>
    A recognizer that allows to match a prepared recognizer (possibly repeatedly).
    UpperCaseStartIdentifierMatcher
    Matches identifiers that start with a upper case letter and only contain letters and numbers.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EShallowEntityType
    The possible types of ShallowEntitys.

This package provides the basic framework we use for implementing the shallow parsers.
